---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-secondary text-white mt-16">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-3">ChinaGuide.ai</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Practical, verified travel guides for foreigners visiting China. Written and verified by real travelers.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-400 mb-3">Quick Links</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li><a href="/guides" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-white transition-colors">Travel Guides</a></li>
          <li><a href="/apps" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-white transition-colors">Essential Apps</a></li>
          <li><a href="/guides/visa-types" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-white transition-colors">Visa Information</a></li>
          <li><a href="/guides/mobile-payment" class="text-gray-300 hover:text-white transition-colors">Mobile Payment</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-400 mb-3">About</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          All content is regularly verified against official sources. Information changes frequently — check the verification date on each guide.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-gray-600 mt-8 pt-6 text-center text-gray-400 text-sm">
      &copy; {year} ChinaGuide.ai. Content verified by real travelers.
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
